Go gave me her amused face, both elbows on the bar, hands cradling chin, hunkering down for an incisive dissection of my marriage. Go, an expert panel of one. \'91What about her?\'92\
\
\'91Bad day. It\'92s just a bad day.\'92\
\
\'91Don\'92t let her worry you.\'92 Go lit a cigarette. She smoked exactly one a day. \'91Women are crazy.\'92 Go didn\'92t consider herself part of the general category of women, a word she used derisively.\
